{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1661810/extras/Sin_t\u00edtulo.gif?t=1638465934\" /><br><br><strong>Abi wakes up without memory on a somewhat strange island, perhaps somewhat magical, where thanks to the help of a celestial light, she will be able to overcome various puzzles and reach places never thought of.<br><br>Undoubtedly a story of love and fantastic friendship where you will have to discover the mystery of the place and recover all your memories by finding small fragments scattered throughout the island.</strong><br><br><strong>Play with the two characters.</strong><br><br><strong>When you play with <u>&quot;soul&quot;</u> you can move freely around the place, to anticipate dangers, activate magical mechanisms and help Abi in various situations.<br><br>When you play as <u>&quot;Abi&quot;</u> soul will follow you to protect you and guide yourself in any circumstance. When she moves away from you you can call her with a hiss and she will immediately fly to your side.</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Main features:</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>For fans of Journey, Firewatch and Shelter.<br></li><li>An emotional and intimate story by a one-man team with an unforgettable ending.<br></li><li>Use two characters with completely different mechanics to overcome puzzles.<br></li><li>Enjoy the incredible soundtrack.<br></li><li>A short game (about an hour and a half), focused on the story, with a bit of light puzzle solving and platforming.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Friendly rabbit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1661810/d5b59c734f3ae4aa6a23b5478264d6831fad4444.jpg"},{"name":"Animals","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1661810/9640ae88b1540c57074f4f6072b7f9d9d58a0ed5.jpg"},{"name":"An infinite love","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1661